for a sponsor, some executive level

58
00:02:36.230 --> 00:02:38.320
enthusiast who will support your efforts

59
00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:39.870
throw some budget your way

60
00:02:39.870 --> 00:02:41.810
and help you make progress.

61
